ack.title: Acknowledgments
ack.p: We thank Dr. Darunee Buddhari, staff at Kamphaeng Phet-AFRIMS Virology Research Unit (KAVRU), and villagers in Kamphaeng Phet, Thailand for their support. We also thank Dr. Thanyalak Fansiri, Arissara Pongsiri, Udom Kijchalao, Somsak Tiang-trong, and all staff in Vector Biology and Control section, Department of Entomology, AFRIMS for mosquito collection. Material has been reviewed by the Walter Reed Army Institute of Research. There is no objection to its publication. The opinions or assertions contained herein are the private views of the author, and are not to be construed as official, or as reflecting true views of the Department of the Army or the Department of Defense.
